Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.70,0:02:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.40,0:02:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳會原諒我無禮的突然到訪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.00,0:02:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭德爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.00,0:02:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾在法國沒遇見妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...喔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.70,0:02:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有品味的室內設計呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.00,0:02:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.60,0:02:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來拜訪我 我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是到底有甚麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把東西放在那裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.20,0:03:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太繁忙 差點就忘記了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是生日一定得選最好的禮物送妳才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.30,0:03:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.70,0:03:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是我挑選的佳品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尺寸當然也沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.50,0:03:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的事沒有什麼我是不知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭德爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.40,0:03:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在討論尺寸之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.80,0:03:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你犯了最基本的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.00,0:03:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.10,0:03:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生日是3月14日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道現在是哪個月嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是7月呀 7月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.80,0:03:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你忘記了也不該這麼離譜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是 明日香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.30,0:03:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我是來向妳討禮物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.60,0:04:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能得「妳和我共渡一段時光」的禮物嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.00,0:04:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然跟我想的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這顏色很適合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.70,0:04:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那只戒指不適合這套洋裝呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.50,0:04:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只一定比較適合呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭德爾 有點過火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.60,0:04:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是身為你的朋友來和你慶祝生日的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你的玩笑太過分的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是開玩笑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.50,0:04:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 現在是最佳機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想錯過這個機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.10,0:04:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳和隼人吵架了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.70,0:04:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 妳對他會失望是理所當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的時候很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.60,0:05:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的時候就就拿旁人出氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己犯錯也不承認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.90,0:05:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任性 傲慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為車手或者身為男子漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那種是最差勁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭德爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那種傢伙擺弄 斥責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.90,0:05:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實在是看不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.40,0:05:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的 蘭德爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我太多嘴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.50,0:05:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人是拿過兩次世界冠軍的賽車手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.90,0:05:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對賽車是門外漢的我不該對賽車的事指手畫腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳講的話並沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.60,0:05:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是有沒有錯的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.50,0:05:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車隊和媒體已經給隼人很大壓力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.80,0:05:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不該再說那種給隼人增添壓力的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.90,0:06:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我應該說妳也變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.00,0:06:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想要對他更溫柔體貼是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.00,0:06:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這種東西對現在的他毫無幫助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.50,0:06:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我是無所謂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.30,0:06:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只會使他脫離現狀的可能性就變得更低罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.20,0:06:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喪失了身為車手最重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.80,0:06:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到連妳也沒有發現這點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.60,0:06:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗利茲慢下來了!發生甚麼事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四個優勝落空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗利茲的AL-ZARD進入工作站了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣想都覺得有古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.70,0:06:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的解釋就是跑車真的有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這種事不大可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.70,0:06:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子是每場比賽都有檢查的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.40,0:06:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.20,0:07:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾怎樣看也不像是個厲害的賽車手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.30,0:07:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的賽車經驗跟你比起來有等於沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.60,0:07:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的他 突然在閃電霹靂車裡有那種表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我就是難以相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.40,0:07:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他使用的是生化電腦嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.70,0:07:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.50,0:07:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單靠換個嚮導系統就能使賽車手就能變成超人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當老闆就不用那麼辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2018年最後一戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.70,0:07:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在預賽裡突破風見隼人的極速紀錄時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.80,0:07:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候你的吼聲我是不會忘記的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.20,0:07:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你和極限搏鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.90,0:07:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在和你的極限挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是高速的恐懼與賭上你的所有一切\N搏鬥時的吼聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.10,0:07:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連經驗和技術一流的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躋身頂級車手行列的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跑出那個速度都那麼艱難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管再怎樣進化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.90,0:08:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是改了個嚮導系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.70,0:08:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以使一個新人輕易達到那速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上有這麼荒謬的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸妳一籌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我們的確不是傀儡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會犯錯 會感到恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.90,0:08:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他什麼錯也不犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連跑的路線都好不紊亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.50,0:08:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都露出輕鬆的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說奇怪 確實是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.30,0:08:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是機器人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.50,0:08:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.90,0:08:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 幹嗎真的打呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲是遊戲 比賽是比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會手下留情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.70,0:08:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!既然那樣 我也不手下留情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.10,0:09:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0080,,{\bord0}美國 佛羅里達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.00,0:09:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 等一下 把球還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.70,0:09:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.40,0:09:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喪失了身為車手最重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到連妳也沒有發現這點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.70,0:09:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都玩得很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.80,0:10:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.20,0:10:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃...我知道訓練很重要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但偶爾也該散散心嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.70,0:10:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得哥哥排出時間給你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.10,0:10:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒說我需要放假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想玩的是明日香你們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.10,0:10:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我沒有時間悠閒地享受假期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車隊也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來散心又怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.40,0:10:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海邊玩又改不了車子性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我們玩的時候...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.20,0:10:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.70,0:10:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳抱怨也是沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.90,0:10:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.10,0:10:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼去看車賽好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.30,0:10:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車賽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.50,0:10:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼車賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說新條也有出場哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.30,0:10:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是普通型汽車賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通型汽車?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美貴寫信過來有提到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢!果然是今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去 我沒興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.90,0:11:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通型賽車和我賽車的類別完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.30,0:11:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了也沒什麼收穫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.60,0:11:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是... 新條也有出場啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也很久沒見到美貴...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.00,0:11:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳叫我和他們見面敘舊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我現在的成績搞不好還會遭到嘲笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.10,0:11:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.10,0:11:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那麼討厭放假的話就快滾回日本去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.80,0:11:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪費大家的假期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.20,0:11:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家擔心你 看你臉色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手曬得好紅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.70,0:11:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快塗防曬油就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的飯一直沒收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.10,0:12:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.00,0:12:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭!拉鏈卡住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.50,0:12:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.80,0:12:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.10,0:12:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎可以...請溫柔點...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.30,0:12:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.90,0:12:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0080,,{\bord0}佛羅里達州 迪特拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.00,0:12:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車號26 史蒂芬．福利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.80,0:12:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上來的是車號8號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前年度冠軍的傑法．金格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.80,0:12:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換了車隊以後自信滿滿的奧裡巴利也佔到了好位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.70,0:12:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是最近漸入佳境的車號48
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.70,0:12:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前閃電霹靂車冠軍 日本的新條直輝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.50,0:12:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下8圈 各車速度加速了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.80,0:13:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.00,0:13:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,48號車新條的車子一直追上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擠進領先的車群中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...真的是新條?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.80,0:13:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候古雷格真是太丟臉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.70,0:13:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 可是不會這樣就完的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一場比賽會贏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給新條就十拿九穩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.60,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 讓你們來這麼吵的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.20,0:14:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我們打擾你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.00,0:14:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣 還要多謝你們來看我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.80,0:14:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在放假嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.40,0:14:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得第四戰才剛結束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.90,0:14:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀他怎樣了?是不是癱在一邊一直發牢騷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.70,0:14:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是有講類似的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要是我也被開除就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以他的性格我早料到會那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.50,0:14:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美貴妳變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.20,0:14:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.00,0:14:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我變得更壯一點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.30,0:14:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫他讓我在這裡經歷了那麼多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.50,0:14:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為什麼要參加普通汽車比賽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.40,0:14:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以新條的資歷\N大可以去任何優秀的閃電霹靂車車隊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.30,0:14:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直輝一開始也像加賀一樣喊著要參加獎金車賽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.30,0:15:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直輝？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.70,0:15:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美貴說那畢竟太魯莽了 阻止了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.20,0:15:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美貴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.20,0:15:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎金車賽...為甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣說好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.80,0:15:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想把自己的過去全部扔掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直輝是大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.70,0:15:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到什麼就一股腦完全往那邊衝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起哦 我就是笨嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.80,0:15:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為那部AL-ZARD和弗利茲的出現而被解雇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.30,0:15:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雲社長當時指出了我許多缺點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.10,0:15:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我無法坦白承認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.80,0:15:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想如果我駕駛那部車我也會贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.50,0:15:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而 覺得到這裡賽車的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始我也是滿腦子在想車子的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.80,0:15:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為沒有性能好的車的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這時候我被美貴大罵了一頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.10,0:16:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有說啊 妳說「你沒有好車就無法開車了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.50,0:16:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不就表示你的頭腦與技術沒有用處了？」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.40,0:16:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我沒說錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.60,0:16:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 車子性能好連一年級的學生都能跑贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是賽車是那樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是製造高速車的遊戲競賽嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那種東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.50,0:16:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確為了取勝或許要有跑得快的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.20,0:16:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是車賽不光是看車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛的人是我們呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是職業車手的我在駕駛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.90,0:16:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以玩普通汽車也不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那絕對是靠車手的技術決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不太需要花錢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.80,0:16:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去我跑的諸多車賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.80,0:16:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不是跑不贏比賽的車手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.20,0:17:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我有信心去克服\N一切惡劣條件與車子性能差異的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會回閃電霹靂車賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後擊敗他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.30,0:17:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 到時的直輝會很強喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.60,0:17:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是你 或許也不會那樣輕易取勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.90,0:17:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.50,0:18:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...一定要向妳道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在巴西時對你說的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.70,0:18:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其它很多...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.30,0:18:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.80,0:18:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...到底一直在做甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不是在比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.40,0:18:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是開車而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.70,0:18:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被AL-ZARD凌駕之後 非常焦急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿大家當出氣筒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.60,0:18:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.40,0:18:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.20,0:18:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新條面前...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不敢正視他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.70,0:18:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 看著你痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻什麼也幫不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或許是在逃避 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.40,0:18:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心想這始終只是隼人你的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.50,0:18:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該更認真地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.30,0:18:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起想辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.10,0:18:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像美貴那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.60,0:19:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳會原諒我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.10,0:19:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是你非勝不可的心情引發出來的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.50,0:19:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.90,0:19:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.30,0:19:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.10,0:19:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.00,0:19:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的演出效果用在和解的結局上是太過火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.20,0:20:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見5.2秒就離開工作站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.00,0:20:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在以第六的排名回到車道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.10,0:20:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領先的仍是葵的菲爾．弗利茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.60,0:20:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二位是卡爾．里胥特．馮．蘭德爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.50,0:20:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三位是法蘭茲．海尼爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著是加賀和古利特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.50,0:20:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那後面是風見隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗利茲跑到第48圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.70,0:20:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來西班牙杯的優勝又是他的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.00,0:20:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.40,0:20:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!今天就由我來掩護你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.10,0:20:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩....請等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.00,0:20:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我掩護你呀...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.40,0:20:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是車賽不光是看車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.40,0:20:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛的人是我們呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.50,0:20:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是職業車手的我在駕駛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.00,0:21:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我也不是只靠車子性能與運氣拿下兩個冠軍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.40,0:21:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上了 要去了!阿斯拉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.20,0:21:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人那傢伙今天氣勢這麼強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的傢伙到前面來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.60,0:21:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 轉彎的地方有出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.30,0:21:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.20,0:21:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也很不願指責 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是雷歐．安哈特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.70,0:21:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波及到了競爭第四的加賀和風見的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣三輛車都要退出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.40,0:21:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個大飯桶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.00,0:21:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆斷手算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.40,0:21:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了世人好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.00,0:22:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實在是輸給那個新人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.30,0:22:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他非把別人拖下水才高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.20,0:22:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.50,0:22:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.90,0:22:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日子小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.90,0:22:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.00,0:22:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她剛才還和名雲社長在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.60,0:22:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在車房裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.90,0:22:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.20,0:22:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.10,0:22:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難得 這裡竟然一個人也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.10,0:22:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼啊 從未見過的飲料？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.10,0:22:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.60,0:22:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.60,0:23:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.00,0:23:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙真現實喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.00,0:23:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一和明日香和好就馬上變得這麼有精神起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.30,0:23:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別說奇怪的話啦 好嗎 真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.80,0:23:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別生氣 別生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.10,0:23:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你有沒有看見今日子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.40,0:23:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我看見她向駕駛沙龍的方向去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.80,0:23:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那麼 我去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.40,0:23:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 隼人 拿一支
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.30,0:23:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.10,0:23:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.50,0:23:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是營養飲料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.40,0:23:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒體力是會被明日香討厭喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.90,0:23:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.20,0:23:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.40,0:23:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀不論什麼時候都是很匆忙的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.10,0:23:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.50,0:23:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.90,0:23:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得有這段空閒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.30,0:23:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吃好吃的東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.90,0:23:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.40,0:23:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 難喝死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.70,0:24:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是弗利茲勝出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.80,0:24:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 那傢伙真的很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.20,0:24:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要快點想辦法才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.70,0:24:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人!你開得太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.00,0:24:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不應該啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.00,0:24:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.50,0:24:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.40,0:24:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 是的 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.10,0:24:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你還是小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.60,0:24:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次發現就不能放過你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:55.80,0:24:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.40,0:24:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.80,0:25:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有打算要開那麼快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.40,0:25:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為是80公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.00,0:25:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說那是80公里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.40,0:25:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑!速度表都快爆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.30,0:25:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.80,0:25:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的速度感覺應該沒錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.60,0:25:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之換我來駕駛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.90,0:25:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 下次我會小心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.10,0:25:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:31.50,0:25:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 我肚子餓扁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.20,0:25:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.30,0:25:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在小心翼翼地駕駛 別囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.10,0:25:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 比烏龜還要慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.70,0:25:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 妳在做甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.60,0:25:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我稍微跟你開玩笑一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.10,0:25:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也不要這麼亂來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:54.40,0:25:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,減速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.80,0:25:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.60,0:26:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停車!!停車!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.40,0:26:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人!你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.30,0:26:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 隼人
